{"tid":913780,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[日韓大戰]「防彈JIMIN本人道歉了！」　日電視台捏造假聞惹怒韓網","createTime":"2018-11-23T16:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T20:46:15.000Z","uid":74065,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"15313695e0173e54c8b52fb3d715f1c63b9e7212","tid":913780,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T16:06:47.000Z","msg":"南韓團體防彈少年團成員JIMIN（朴智旻）因1年前穿韓國光復節紀念T恤，上頭的原爆雲圖案意外成為政治事件，所屬經紀公司日前已聲明表示，絕無特殊意圖，但對於因此而受到傷害的人感到非常抱歉，<span style=\"color: red;\">不過日本TBS電視台節目《Akko ni omakase!》卻報導了他本人在演唱會上道歉的假消息。</span><br />\n<br />\n 節目《Akko ni omakase!》在18日播出的節目中，播送防彈少年團在東京巨蛋開唱的畫面，打上：「JIMIN在日本公演上，為穿著原爆T恤事件道歉了。」的字幕，<span style=\"color: red;\">並聲稱JIMIN本人說，不僅日本粉絲，讓全世界的粉絲都擔心了，「特別對不起日本粉絲。」</span><br />\n<br />\n 不過，韓媒指出，JIMIN在演唱會上僅表示：「很多事情不僅讓ARMY（防彈少年團粉絲名 ），也讓許多人受驚且擔心了&hellip;，心很痛。」，<span style=\"color: red;\">並沒有直指爭議事件，更沒有指名向日本粉絲道歉。韓媒23日報導此消息時直言日節目是「捏造事實」，南韓網友也大多表示不能接受，反要該節目道歉。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3716/d3716157.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3716%2Fd3716157.jpg&h=2823cfbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼TBS電視台節目指JIMIN本人在演唱會上向日本粉絲道歉。<br />\n（圖／翻攝自韓網、讀者提供)<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3693/d3693631.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3693%2Fd3693631.jpg&h=e15a652e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3687/d3687109.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3687%2Fd3687109.jpg&h=5ec8f7e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲JIMIN穿著的T恤上印有原爆雲圖案，意外演變成政治事件。<br />\n（圖／翻攝自YouTube、OURHISTORY官網）"},{"pid":"75598c8042c5f49cebfd1f757ce66958e5a1ad94","tid":913780,"uid":213300,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T16:07:56.000Z","msg":"最慘就係扯埋我地twice落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2e6d898341cefb5d3eca88572f791563d1787e","tid":913780,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"75598c8042c5f49cebfd1f757ce66958e5a1ad94","tid":913780,"uid":213300,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T16:07:56.000Z","msg":"最慘就係扯埋我地twice落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T16:10:20.000Z","msg":"冇啦啦燒埋多賢唔知想點LO"},{"pid":"f1e94be607109acb20f95064f243cb8a1801ffda","tid":913780,"uid":4574,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T16:13:30.000Z","msg":"點解要道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你韓泡被日本仔<br />\n捉去做慰安婦<br />\n唔通又要道歉"},{"pid":"37c336d20bf7f894c249ce268e4838c069d6e9c8","tid":913780,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f1e94be607109acb20f95064f243cb8a1801ffda","tid":913780,"uid":4574,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T16:13:30.000Z","msg":"點解要道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你韓泡被日本仔<br />\n捉去做慰安婦<br />\n唔通又要道歉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T20:24:15.000Z","msg":"因為日本比韓狗優秀所以韓狗要道歉囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"610ddf86f6a3f2459c01caf4338dc06fbdae1d0c","tid":913780,"uid":33077,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T20:32:11.000Z","msg":"太遲啦 之前經理人公司講到一樣還一樣呢d 態度<br />\n應該要收爐啦(至少日本市場)"},{"pid":"ae15cb5f24b6165c5ae224ac19710d3cbaf21fc0","tid":913780,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T20:46:15.000Z","msg":"抵啦呢條柒碌 明知日狗玻璃心仲咁玩"}]}